  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd -\u00a0\u0bb0\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0baf \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The new government will carry out necessary measures for economic recovery - Russian Foreign Minister believes",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Russian Foreign Minister Maria Zakharova has stated that the current situation in Sri Lanka, including the incidents reported in recent times, is an internal matter of the country. She also stated that she believes that the new government of Sri Lanka will take the necessary steps to recover the country's economy from the crisis situation.",
        "The Russian Foreign Minister has expressed the above opinion in the background of the political crisis in the country due to the self-insurgency of the people following the economic crisis in Sri Lanka.",
        "Accordingly, the current incidents in Sri Lanka are the country's internal affairs. As a friendly country, we believe that Sri Lanka's political processes should be carried out in accordance with its constitution and existing laws,' said the Russian Foreign Minister.",
        "He expressed his hope that the current situation will soon return to normalcy as predicted, and also stated that he believes that the new government of Sri Lanka will take the necessary steps to recover the country's economy from the crisis situation.",
        "Sri Lanka has deepened its ties with Russia in the last few years. Therefore, amid the current economic crisis, Sri Lanka is dependent on Russia for the country's essential fuel imports. Therefore, it is noteworthy that Sri Lanka has announced that it will not take any side in this matter, despite the fact that many countries of the world have expressed their condemnation of the Russian invasion of Ukraine."
      ],
